name: No Future- Anthropology of a high school party
description:
No Future- Anthropology of a high school party, 2022, Video, 18s

This piece depicts the typical alpha male in his natural habitat during an American high school party in the late 1990's.  See how he expresses his superiority by finding a smaller creature to subdue.  This piece is from the "No Future" series of digital work. It examines our daily lives and socialization in the digital world.  See more at www.laladrona.com
